snippet.title: SWARM 2 - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
SWARM 2, the highly anticipated sequel to SWARM is out now on Meta Quest 2 + 3!

 An electrifying rogue-like shooter with epic new environments, intoxicating progression, and globally competitive leaderboards - this is what VR is really made for!
